text: Bygones () is a 1987 Dutch drama film directed by Ine Schenkkan. It is based on the book of the same name of Inez Dullemen. https://www.volkskrant.nl/nieuws-achtergrond/een-vakvrouw-zonder- carrieredrang~bfd4205a/ The film won the Golden Calf for Best Feature Film award at the 1987 Netherlands Film Festival. Jasperina de Jong also won the Golden Calf for Best Actress for her role in the film.https://www.filmfestival.nl/archief/vroeger-is-dood/ == References == == External links == * Category:1987 films Category:Dutch drama films Category:Dutch films Category:Dutch-language films Category:1987 drama films
